You will need to customize the following files to configure ejabberd for
local use:

    ${PKG_SYSCONFDIR}/ejabberd.defaults
    ${PKG_SYSCONFDIR}/ejabberd.inetrc
    ${PKG_SYSCONFDIR}/ejabberd.cfg

